cs.DL, cs.IR, cs.SE, cs.CY, cs.CR

This paper discusses the tracking and analysis of data and software citations, which falls under the category of digital libraries (cs.DL) and information retrieval (cs.IR). The focus on software citation principles and recommendations suggests a connection to software engineering (cs.SE), while the use of DOIs and measurement of impact relates to cybernetics (cs.CY) and cryptography (cs.CR).
